<v-container fill-height>
    <v-layout align-center justify-center>
        <v-flex xs12 sm8 md4>
            <v-card class="elevation-12">
                <v-toolbar dark color="purple darken-4">
                    <v-toolbar-title>Join Form</v-toolbar-title>
                </v-toolbar>
                <v-card-text>
                    <v-form ref="form" v-model="valid" lazy-validation>
                        <v-text-field
                            prepend-icon="person"
                            name="email"
                            label="Email"
                            type="email"
                            v-model="email"
                            :rules="emailRules"
                            required
                        >
                        </v-text-field>
                        <v-text-field
                            prepend-icon="lock"
                            name="password"
                            label="Password"
                            id="password"
                            type="password"
                            required
                            v-model="password"
                            :rules="passwordRules"
                        >
                        </v-text-field>
                    </v-form>
                </v-card-text>
                <v-card-actions>
                    <v-spacer></v-spacer>
                    <v-btn
                        color="primary"
                        :disabled="!valid"
                        @click="submit"
                        >Join</v-btn
                    >
                </v-card-actions>
            </v-card>
        </v-flex>
    </v-layout>
</v-container>
